684-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-1013\" \/><\/a>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<figcaption class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-1013'>\n\t\t\t\tQ&#038;A and Skype\n\t\t\t\t<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>It&#8217;s over, and it&#8217;s a new world record. Farset Labs has contributed to the Worlds Largest Game Jam, and everyone involved should be very proud of what they&#8217;ve accomplished in just 48 hours. With 30 registered Jammers, 11 registered games (6 made it to submission, but that&#8217;s ok!), no-one can say that Northern Ireland doesn&#8217;t [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":1032,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[136],"tags":[92,711,714,12,713,698,715,706,699],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/blog.farsetlabs.org.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1000"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/blog.farsetlabs.org.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/blog.farsetlabs.org.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/blog.farsetlabs.org.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/blog.farsetlabs.org.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1000"}],"version-history":[{"count":5,"href":"https:\/\/blog.farsetlabs.org.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1000\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1034,"href":"https:\/\/blog.farsetlabs.org.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1000\/revisions\/1034"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/blog.farsetlabs.org.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1032"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/blog.farsetlabs.org.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1000"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/blog.farsetlabs.org.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1000